South Africa beats England 32-12 to win its third Rugby World Cup title
02 Nov 2019, 10:55 by EndPlay
YOKOHAMA, Japan - YOKOHAMA, Japan (AP) - South Africa beats England 32-12 to win its third Rugby World Cup title .
